snippet.title: Warside - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Warside releases on January 28th, 2025!

Welcome to Warside, the fast-paced turn-based tactics game. With a single-player story campaign, multiplayer support, and a built-in map editor, the fight for victory never ends. Choose your Commander, assemble your forces, and battle your way to victory.

Visit us at:
https://firstbreaklabs.com/ 

Wishlist our games on Steam!
Baseless:     https://store.steampowered.com/app/1129260/Baseless/
Entropy Survivors:     https://store.steampowered.com/app/2602030/Entropy_Survivors/
Particle Hearts:     https://store.steampowered.com/app/2074740/Particle_Hearts/
Warside:     https://store.steampowered.com/app/2368300/Warside/

Follow us on our socials!
